channel.title: How do i fix this dupe please help [PI]
channel.description: Okay heres how the dupe goes down, they change the client.class in the client, and it creats commands like ::ags and gives 999m ags's too the person who has the hacked client, how do i fix this please help!

item.title: How do i fix this dupe please help [PI]
item.dc:creator: @T41 t4
item.description:
@T41 wrote:

[quote=“youda fucking best, post:5, topic:400119”][quote author=orcashark link=topic=497209.msg3635676#msg3635676 date=1308589592]

What the fuck am I reading.

+1
[/quote]

Guys don’t be smart ass’s, this is legit, i’m getting duped by someone that’s editing my client files, and making them be able too spawn items in game.[/quote]
Client sided hacks do not effect server-side data, unless of course it were to spoof packets (which there’s nothing really on the client’s outgoing packets that could yield this result provided you’re not a complete idiot and check that the packet’s information is valid).
